Joe Biden Could Easily Recall the Billions in Military Equipment Police Received From the Pentagon 
 
By 
    Stephen Semler  
 
American police departments are armed to the teeth with military-grade weaponry like Humvees and assault rifles. Nothing is stopping President Biden from shutting down this military-to-police pipeline right away. 
 
Nearly $34 million in military equipment was sent to police in the first quarter of 2021. (Jonathan Wiggs/The Boston Globe via Getty Images) 
 
